reviewText: This movie  is really NOT worth the price I paid for it.  When it starts to get informative and you think you are about to see an example of the tombs, THERE is none.  The statues along the causeway are great but there is little else to see.  I there was a money back guarantee I would have asked for it immediately.  IT IS NOT WORTH THE TIME.. Infomercials have more content than this DVD.  Don't waste your money.
